name: Happy Melffys
effect:
2+ Level 2 monsters
Once per turn, you can also Xyz Summon "Happy Melffys" by using 1 "Melffy" monster you control with a different name as Xyz Material. (If you used an Xyz Monster, any Xyz Materials attached to it also become Xyz Materials on this card.). (Quick Effect): You can Tribute this Xyz Summoned card; Special Summon 1"Melffy" Xyz Monster from your Extra Deck, then you can attach cards from any field and/or GY(s) to that Special Summoned monster as material, up to the number of materials this card had.
